  "texts": [
    "The average coverage score of the five assessment criteria was 3.93 (min = 2.79, max = 4.90).",
    "The coverage of each assessment criterion by method is shown in Fig. 4b.",
    "Examining the results by assessment criteria revealed interesting patterns.",
    "Construction Functionality (Supplementary Table 7): The majority of the methods (81.3%; n = 13) included functionality to download data, while 56.3% (n = 9) were able to process experimental data and 37.5% (n = 6) were able to process clinical data.",
    "Availability (Supplementary Table 8): Three-fourths of the methods (75%; n = 12) were written in Python and 43.8% (n = 7) were written in a Java-based language."
